Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神感应线路上传来数据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始解释
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主殿下的指引
